            <span class="a11y">Series: </span>
            <span class="promo-series__title">School Wars:</span>
                        <span class="promo-series__tagline">How Battles Over Vouchers, Book Bans, COVID-19 and More Are Harming Public Education</span>
                    </h3>
    </div>
    
